<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٦ - <span class="c2">(٢٤٤٤)</span> حَدَّثَنَاهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3889">أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">وَكِيعٌ </a>. <span class="c2">(ح)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4206">عُبَيْدُ اللهِ بْنُ مُعَاذٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6217">أَبِي </a>-<span class="c5"> قَالَا:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2287">سَعْدٍ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ مِثْلَهُ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>